				<div style="font-style:italic">I think just a pool of mods who are authorized to act in any forum would be preferable, keep it simple.  Most of the concerns we had regarding mods not knowing the sub-culture of the smaller forums turns out to be moot since those forums are typically well-behaved and the only reports that come out of them are for spam.</div>
			
